headline.main: Leader of Finland's Eurosceptic Party to Step Down
headline.print_headline: Leader of Finland's Eurosceptic Party to Step Down

lead_paragraph: Finnish foreign minister Timo Soini said on Sunday he would step down as leader of the nationalist and eurosceptic Finns party in June, a move which could challenge the future of the country's three-party government.
